originalText.text: Went for brunch, my experience personally was not great. My food was good I had the Rasta pasta with chicken, the rum punch was okay! The bartender Rose has a disgusting attitude and really shouldn’t be working in a customer service environment. She was very rude,and just overall uncalled for.  I understand we all have bad days but people come to places for the experience not bad vibes and she ruined it for my family and I. Aisha the manager was super sweet, I think this place is fairly new so I give them that but there was just a lot going on during the brunch hour and it just seemed unorganized
